comment: I read somewhere their was a clue in cult for apocalypse. Apparently the Manwhich that Ally makes for Kai was a clue for Man Witch (warlock) could just be a coincidence tho
I think an alien season would be sooo easy to do; AHS: Roswell? come on we’ve even had the “Battle Los Angeles” incident they could tie it into—

I'm a few days late to the party but had a question for you Mary about season 8. I definitely enjoyed Cordelia in season 8, but do you think Sarah's portrayal in 8 is the same as it was in season 3? It kinda felt like it wasn't quite the same character. I'm just nitpicking though.
American Horror Story: Myth needs to be a thing. It can be about Mythical Creatures, Urban Legends, Conspiracy Theories, Serial Killers, and of course the Aliens.
